Package: tweetscores
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the Estimation of Ideology Scores with Twitter Data
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2016-06-20
Author: Pablo Barbera <pablo.barbera@nyu.edu>
Maintainer: Pablo Barbera <pablo.barbera@nyu.edu>
Description: This package provides a series of functions to collect and analyze Twitter data, and to estimate the ideological positions of Twitter users with the method described in Barbera (2015, Political Analysis).
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R2WinBUGS
Imports: yaml, httr, jsonlite, ROAuth, ggplot2
